Invoices and Receipts are in CAS, follows same pattern as PAD/ONLINE BANKING/ROUTING SLIPS

Maintenance / OPS is harder
More complex - Unmapping for short name is more complex (reverse the receipt and adjust invoice to zero in CFS)
